# ILOs for this week

- Discuss the social and cultural roles and experiences of women
- Discuss the gender health gap
- Consider policies and laws that disproportionately affect women

# Social and cultural roles of women

stigma

Bronfenbrenner's model of gender development - social factors influencing development

Changes over time (i.e. historical differences to present day)

Changes over the lifecourse

Cultural lens -in less individualistic, more collectivist cultures, there's a focus on the whole family taking care of offspring; in western cultures, the sociohistorical framework is that women are the main caretakers (although this thinking is changing)

